+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+
|          Semtech SX1243 firmware for STM8L152C6						  |
+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+

This firmware currently supports the following Semtech product:
	- SX1243

1. Introduction
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

This is RF remote controller project for BHAGYASHREE INDUSTRIES (India). 
This is transmitter part which we promote them Semtech SX1243.   	

2. Version history
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

<master> - This is original project from STM8L_Discovery_SX1278_SFM1L project.
<1.0.0> - Port Semtech SX1243 referece driver into STM8L_Discovery project.
